The paper focuses on the iterative process of developing machine learning workflows with humans-in-the-loop, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), software engineering (cs.SE), and cybersecurity (cs.CY) to ensure the security and privacy of the data being used.
